{"word":"ἐγγίζω","slug":"ἐγγίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐγγίζω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐγγύς\">ἐγγύς</a></el>] in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> only <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ intr.\">intr.</a> <b>come/draw near, approach<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> spatially <b><a href='B:470 21:1'>Mt 21:1</a>; <a href='B:470 26:46'>26:46</a>; <a href='B:490 7:12'>Lk 7:12</a>; <a href='B:510 9:3'>Ac 9:3</a>; <a href='B:650 7:19'>Hb 7:19</a>; <a href='B:660 4:8'>Js 4:8</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> temporally <b><a href='B:470 3:2'>Mt 3:2</a></b> (of God’s kingdom, and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> in the Synoptists); <b><a href='B:470 21:34'>21:34</a>; <a href='B:470 26:45'>26:45</a>; <a href='B:490 21:8'>Lk 21:8</a>; <a href='B:490 22:1'>22:1</a>; <a href='B:510 7:17'>Ac 7:17</a>; <a href='B:520 13:12'>Ro 13:12</a>; <a href='B:570 2:30'>Phil 2:30</a></b> (<el>μέχρι ϑανάτου ἐ.</el> come close to dying); <b><a href='B:660 5:8'>Js 5:8</a>; <a href='B:670 4:7'>1 Pt 4:7</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐγγέγραμμαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐγγράφω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}